AMC Theatres® delivers distinctive and affordable 
		movie-going experiences throughout the United States.
We maintain a significant presence in the top 50 DMAs, including the 
		number one or two market share in each of the top 15 DMAs, which includes 
		New York, Los Angeles, Chicago, Philadelphia, San Francisco, Atlanta and 
		Dallas. The company operates 22 of the 50 highest grossing theatres in the 
		United States, including four of the top five.
